          "process_md": "**Step 1:** Visit the official [website ](https://textiles.odisha.gov.in/onlineservice/)to Register yourself.\n**Step 2:** Fill in all your details in the registration window and click on &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot;Submit&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot; and a message will be displayed for successful registration.\n**Step 3:** Now click on “Go to Login”.  Enter the same username &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp; password used during account creation then Click on &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot;Login&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot;.\n**Step 4:** Select the scheme as &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot;Mukhyamantri Bayan Jyoti Yojana&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot; from the dropdown menu.\n**Step 5:** A form will open. Fill in all the details and upload all the relevant documents.\n**Step 6:** Select the “Declaration” and click on &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot;Save&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot; button to see preview of the application form.  Click on &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot;Edit&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot; button if you want to edit the application form.\n**Step 7:** Click on “Final Submit” button to generate and receive the OTP in Mobile No. &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp; E-mail ID.\n**Step 8:** Enter the OTP and click on &amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot;Submit&amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;amp;quot; button.\n"
        }
